            <node CREATED="1173534212344" ID="Freemind_Link_437341317" MODIFIED="1174055721276" TEXT="&lt;html&gt;&lt;b&gt;Questions&lt;/b&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&#xa;&lt;li&gt;Why two companies (trust and pharma Co)?&#xa;&lt;li&gt;Where is the future direction of the company?&lt;ul&gt;&#xa;&lt;li&gt;Is it only acquisition, or&#xa;&lt;li&gt;innovation?&lt;/ul&gt;&#xa;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;&quot;It&apos;s very important to come up with a&lt;br&gt;&#xa;pipeline of new products.&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&quot;  How?&#xa;&lt;li&gt;Where are sources of competitive intelligence&lt;br&gt;&#xa;and hence strategic planning&#xa;&lt;ul&gt;&#xa;&lt;li&gt;Aesica, or&#xa;&lt;li&gt;Backers?&lt;/ul&gt;&#xa;&lt;li&gt;What is known about the banker&apos;s portfolio (ie&lt;br&gt;&#xa;do they have any other pharma Cos on their&lt;br&gt;&#xa;books)?&#xa;&lt;li&gt;How important were the wind turbines (ie&lt;br&gt;&#xa;ROCs) to Aesica Cash flow?&#xa;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;US6949650&lt;/b&gt; Who were the inventors?&#xa;&lt;/ul&gt;">
